title: Nassar victims lead each other out of the shadows
text:
Nassar victims lead each other out of the shadows Saturday, February 03, 2018 - 02:16 
The case of Larry Nassar, coming amid an ongoing national debate over sexual misconduct and the #MeToo movement, will likely convince more abuse victims to come forward as their stories are viewed as credible. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
